{
  "id": "69a9307352374518027b5ad3",
  "title": "#inajob の試しに録音してみた talk139: LLMを使った時にで？となる現象・近所の行きつけの店があることの良さ・UIAPduino",
  "created": 1772695673,
  "updated": 1772840962,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a9307352374518027b5ad3",
      "text": "#inajob の試しに録音してみた talk139: LLMを使った時にで？となる現象・近所の行きつけの店があることの良さ・UIAPduino",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695673,
      "updated": 1772695673
    },
    {
      "id": "69a964a1000000000053af9d",
      "text": "[https://open.spotify.com/episode/0x2FA2kciAsWPSixrxWYNa]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772709026,
      "updated": 1772709032
    },
    {
      "id": "69a964a2000000000053af9f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772709027,
      "updated": 1772709027
    },
    {
      "id": "69a964a2000000000053af9e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772709026,
      "updated": 1772709026
    },
    {
      "id": "69a930790000000000cb00f6",
      "text": "準備中",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695674,
      "updated": 1772709026
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9307f0000000000cb00f8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695680,
      "updated": 1772695680
    },
    {
      "id": "69a930b10000000000cb0100",
      "text": "\t[Google Formsで感想を送る https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1fC9gUB6PC3uJidZAJ8pgD1qLiMdvIgZOenrTwcOqpnw/]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695729,
      "updated": 1772695729
    },
    {
      "id": "69a930b10000000000cb0101",
      "text": " [Discordサーバー「inajob川」に参加する https://discord.gg/vHu4CXuMPq]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695729,
      "updated": 1772695729
    },
    {
      "id": "69a930b10000000000cb0102",
      "text": " \t[参加する前に様子を見る https://inajob.github.io/inajob-river-peeker/]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695729,
      "updated": 1772695729
    },
    {
      "id": "69a930b10000000000cb0103",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695729,
      "updated": 1772695729
    },
    {
      "id": "69a930b00000000000cb00ff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695729,
      "updated": 1772695729
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96003000000000053af6e",
      "text": "\t健康",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772707845,
      "updated": 1772707847
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9600a000000000053af70",
      "text": "\t\t花粉を感じる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772707851,
      "updated": 1772707854
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96012000000000053af71",
      "text": "\t\t\t目薬・うがいでしのいでいる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772707859,
      "updated": 1772707867
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96006000000000053af6f",
      "text": "\t\tうがいを丁寧にしている",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772707847,
      "updated": 1772707850
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9309a0000000000cb00fb",
      "text": " LLMを使った時に「で？」となる現象",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695707,
      "updated": 1772698922
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96027000000000053af72",
      "text": " \t生成AIを使ったコーディングで物を作った後に「で？」となる感じがする",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772707879,
      "updated": 1772707892
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9603b000000000053af73",
      "text": " \t\tこれで何をするんだ？ みたいな？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772707900,
      "updated": 1772707905
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9604b000000000053af74",
      "text": " \t昔から役に立たないものなどを趣味で作ってきたが・・",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772707916,
      "updated": 1772707930
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9605b000000000053af75",
      "text": " \t\t[正気になる前に作りきる]([正気になる前にやり切れ])",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772707932,
      "updated": 1772707951
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9606f000000000053af76",
      "text": " \t\t生成AIでも同じ事をしているはずなんだが、感じ方が異なる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772707951,
      "updated": 1772707979
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96098000000000053af77",
      "text": " \t\tコーディング作業自体が楽しい？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772707993,
      "updated": 1772708000
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9609f000000000053af78",
      "text": " \t\tサンクコストの影響で価値が高いと誤認している？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708000,
      "updated": 1772708012
    },
    {
      "id": "69a960ab000000000053af79",
      "text": " \t\t\t酸っぱいブドウの逆",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708012,
      "updated": 1772708015
    },
    {
      "id": "69a960ba000000000053af7a",
      "text": " \tどこで気づくか？という話なのかな？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708027,
      "updated": 1772708035
    },
    {
      "id": "69a960c8000000000053af7b",
      "text": " \tその先にイノベーションがあるのだろうか？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708041,
      "updated": 1772708051
    },
    {
      "id": "69a960d2000000000053af7c",
      "text": " \t\tサンクコスト、コーディングが楽しいからその「谷」を乗り切れたのかな？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708051,
      "updated": 1772708069
    },
    {
      "id": "69a960e5000000000053af7d",
      "text": " \tある程度作りこんだ先に見える風景？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708070,
      "updated": 1772708080
    },
    {
      "id": "69a960ef000000000053af7e",
      "text": " \tいやいや、先のことを考えず作って成功するパターンは少ないんじゃないか？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708080,
      "updated": 1772708102
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9610c000000000053af7f",
      "text": " \t\t早く見切りがつけられてよかったねという話？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708109,
      "updated": 1772708133
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96134000000000053af81",
      "text": " \t自分は何が楽しくてそのプロジェクトを進めているのかを自覚すると良いかもね",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708149,
      "updated": 1772708162
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9615f000000000053af82",
      "text": " 最近LLMで作ったもの",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708192,
      "updated": 1772708196
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96163000000000053af83",
      "text": " \t[cursor]を使った[OpenClaw]みたいなもの",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708196,
      "updated": 1772708208
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9619f000000000053af84",
      "text": " \t\t[https://github.com/jes/cursor-claw/ GitHub - jes/cursor-claw · GitHub]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708256,
      "updated": 1772708259
    },
    {
      "id": "69a961a2000000000053af85",
      "text": "   \tこれをDiscord対応して遊んでみた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708259,
      "updated": 1772708266
    },
    {
      "id": "69a961a9000000000053af86",
      "text": "   [cursor]は無料プランだと50req/month程度しか使えない",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708266,
      "updated": 1772708287
    },
    {
      "id": "69a961be000000000053af87",
      "text": "   日記を読むAIエージェントを作ってみた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708287,
      "updated": 1772708307
    },
    {
      "id": "69a961d5000000000053af89",
      "text": "  ローカルLLM(qwen3-4B)で日記を読むAIエージェント",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708310,
      "updated": 1772708346
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96208000000000053af8b",
      "text": "  \tビジネス用のノートパソコンでもゆっくりなら動かせるという気付き",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708361,
      "updated": 1772708372
    },
    {
      "id": "69a961fa000000000053af8a",
      "text": "  \t無料でやり放題なのは嬉しいが、頭が悪い問題がある",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708347,
      "updated": 1772708360
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9621b000000000053af8c",
      "text": "  ニュースを選別して紹介するAIエージェント",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708380,
      "updated": 1772708393
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96228000000000053af8d",
      "text": "  \t日記から自分の人となりを表す文字列を作り、この人に記事を紹介して というリクエストをLLMに伝える",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708393,
      "updated": 1772708419
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9624c000000000053af8e",
      "text": "  \t↑の人に刺さるキャッチコピーを付けて、というのがなかなか良い",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708429,
      "updated": 1772708441
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96260000000000053af8f",
      "text": "  \t[inajob川]で気が向いた時に動かしている",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708448,
      "updated": 1772708459
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96279000000000053af90",
      "text": "  RakuChordのRaspberry Pi Pico版のファームウェアをMicroPyhtonで書いてみる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708474,
      "updated": 1772708495
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96283000000000053af91",
      "text": "  \t以前はCircuitPythonで作っていた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708484,
      "updated": 1772708501
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96295000000000053af92",
      "text": "  \tMicroPythonのほうがCircuitPythonより速い",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708501,
      "updated": 1772708514
    },
    {
      "id": "69a962a2000000000053af93",
      "text": "  \t\t2コアを活用できる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708515,
      "updated": 1772708519
    },
    {
      "id": "69a962a6000000000053af94",
      "text": "  \t\tViperモードで高速なメモリアクセスが出来る",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708519,
      "updated": 1772708525
    },
    {
      "id": "69a963eb000000000053af95",
      "text": "  [inline]のエディタコンポーネントを[Svelte]で実装してみる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708844,
      "updated": 1772708858
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9647d000000000053af9c",
      "text": "  \t[Svelte]の読み方が怪しい[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708990,
      "updated": 1772708995
    },
    {
      "id": "69a963fa000000000053af96",
      "text": "  \t実装できる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708859,
      "updated": 1772708861
    },
    {
      "id": "69a963fc000000000053af97",
      "text": "  \tReactで書くより短いコードで書けた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708861,
      "updated": 1772708870
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96410000000000053af98",
      "text": "  ブレッドボードエディタ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708881,
      "updated": 1772708889
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96419000000000053af99",
      "text": "  \t[Fritzing]のパーツが利用できるやつ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708890,
      "updated": 1772708907
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6d780000000000787487",
      "text": "  \t[Fritzing]は寄付ウェアで人に勧めづらい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772776825,
      "updated": 1772776855
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6d990000000000787488",
      "text": "  \t パーツデータは使い勝手の良いライセンスで提供されている",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772776858,
      "updated": 1772776871
    },
    {
      "id": "69a96434000000000053af9a",
      "text": "  \t[https://inajob.github.io/protopan/ Protopan - Webブレッドボードエディタ]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772708916,
      "updated": 1772708918
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6db20000000000787489",
      "text": "  作れるんだが、どこで手を止めればよいのかな？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772776883,
      "updated": 1772776940
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6dd0000000000078748a",
      "text": "   メンタルモデルが追いついてない",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772776913,
      "updated": 1772776934
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9309b0000000000cb00fc",
      "text": " 近所の行きつけの店があることの良さ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695707,
      "updated": 1772695707
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6dfa000000000078748b",
      "text": "  近所のメキシコ料理屋の話",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772776956,
      "updated": 1772776970
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6e33000000000078748f",
      "text": "  行くと何かしら面白いイベントがある",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772777011,
      "updated": 1772777020
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6e09000000000078748c",
      "text": "   5歳の娘の幼稚園の友達のご家族と話す",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772776970,
      "updated": 1772777021
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6e19000000000078748d",
      "text": "   同じ会社で働いてる人が常連だった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772776987,
      "updated": 1772777023
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6e28000000000078748e",
      "text": "    気づく前から会っていた！",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772777001,
      "updated": 1772777025
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9309b0000000000cb00fd",
      "text": " [UIAPduino]が盛り上がっている",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695707,
      "updated": 1772698912
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6e680000000000787490",
      "text": "  https://fabscene.com/new/interview/uiapduino-290yen-mass-production-interview/",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772777065,
      "updated": 1772777067
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6e6a0000000000787491",
      "text": "  賛否両論あり",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772777067,
      "updated": 1772777077
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6e780000000000787492",
      "text": "  便乗して和音が鳴るピアノを[UIAPduino]を作った",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772777081,
      "updated": 1772777108
    },
    {
      "id": "69ab680000000000009c493b",
      "text": "  \t[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O8TE0JtaixU]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772840961,
      "updated": 1772840962
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6e930000000000787493",
      "text": "  すでに作ったことがあったのだが、ピンアサインを変更する必要があった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772777108,
      "updated": 1772777124
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6ea40000000000787494",
      "text": "   意外と面倒なのだが、[Gemini CLI]がサッと直してくれた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772777126,
      "updated": 1772777150
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6ecb0000000000787496",
      "text": "  [UIAPduino]の作者の人は[inajob川]の住人",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772777164,
      "updated": 1772777198
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6ef00000000000787497",
      "text": "   あの人と知り合いなんだぜー、というムーブがしたいわけではないのだが、、",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772777201,
      "updated": 1772777219
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6f150000000000787498",
      "text": "   ためろくで話したそうにしてたので、いつかゲストに呼ぼうと考えてる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772777238,
      "updated": 1772777254
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6ebf0000000000787495",
      "text": " 前回",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772777152,
      "updated": 1772777263
    },
    {
      "id": "69a930870000000000cb00fa",
      "text": "\t\t[#inajob の試しに録音してみた talk138: 5歳の娘と伊豆大島旅行]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695688,
      "updated": 1772695696
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9307b0000000000cb00f7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772695676,
      "updated": 1772695676
    }
  ]
}